dict.string:
The fat in meat marked
its energy value. Therefore,
choosing lean meat is
a considerable advantage

Lean meat contains fat,
but it is a different
kind of fat. It is not
depot fat, but structural
fat, being part the membrane
of the muscle, fibres.

This structural fat can
be beneficial to health
as it is polyunsaturated
with both the 'omega-3'
and 'omega-6' kinds of
essential fatty acids
